{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.1","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:1","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Azaria (Ozias), roi de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. 2 Ch 26. (\u00c9s 1:1; 6:1, etc.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La vingt-septi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de J\u00e9roboam, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, Azaria, fils d\u2019Amatsia, roi de Juda, r\u00e9gna.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.2","name":"2 Rois 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.29","name":"2 Rois 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.2","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:2","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il avait seize ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna cinquante-deux ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Jecolia, de J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.3","name":"2 Rois 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.1","name":"2 Rois 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.3","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:3","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, enti\u00e8rement comme avait fait Amatsia, son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.4","name":"2 Rois 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.2","name":"2 Rois 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.4","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:4","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Seulement, les hauts lieux ne disparurent point; le peuple offrait encore des sacrifices et des parfums sur les hauts lieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.5","name":"2 Rois 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.3","name":"2 Rois 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.5","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:5","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel frappa le roi, qui fut l\u00e9preux jusqu\u2019au jour de sa mort et demeura dans une maison \u00e9cart\u00e9e. Et Jotham, fils du roi, \u00e9tait \u00e0 la t\u00eate de la maison et jugeait le peuple du pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.6","name":"2 Rois 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.4","name":"2 Rois 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.6","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:6","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Le reste des actions d\u2019Azaria, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois de Juda?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.7","name":"2 Rois 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.5","name":"2 Rois 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.7","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:7","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Azaria se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et on l\u2019enterra avec ses p\u00e8res dans la ville de David. Et Jotham, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.8","name":"2 Rois 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.6","name":"2 Rois 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.8","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:8","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Zacharie, Schallum, Menahem, Pekachia, P\u00e9kach, rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-12: cf. 2 R 10:30. Am 7:9-11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>La trente-huiti\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Azaria, roi de Juda, Zacharie, fils de J\u00e9roboam, r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 Samarie. Il r\u00e9gna six mois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.9","name":"2 Rois 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.7","name":"2 Rois 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.9","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:9","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, comme avaient fait ses p\u00e8res; il ne se d\u00e9tourna point des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, qui avait fait p\u00e9cher Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.10","name":"2 Rois 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.8","name":"2 Rois 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.10","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:10","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Schallum, fils de Jabesch, conspira contre lui, le frappa devant le peuple, et le fit mourir; et il r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.11","name":"2 Rois 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.9","name":"2 Rois 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.11","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:11","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Zacharie, cela est \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.12","name":"2 Rois 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.10","name":"2 Rois 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.12","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:12","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ainsi s\u2019accomplit ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait d\u00e9clar\u00e9 \u00e0 J\u00e9hu, en disant: Tes fils jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la quatri\u00e8me g\u00e9n\u00e9ration seront assis sur le tr\u00f4ne d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.13","name":"2 Rois 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.11","name":"2 Rois 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.13","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:13","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-31: cf. 1 R 16:8-22. Job 20:5-9. 1 Ch 5:25-26. Os 10:3, 7, 15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Schallum, fils de Jabesch, r\u00e9gna la trente-neuvi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Ozias, roi de Juda. Il r\u00e9gna pendant un mois \u00e0 Samarie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.14","name":"2 Rois 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.12","name":"2 Rois 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.14","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:14","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Menahem, fils de Gadi, monta de Thirtsa et vint \u00e0 Samarie, frappa dans Samarie Schallum, fils de Jabesch, et le fit mourir; et il r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.15","name":"2 Rois 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.13","name":"2 Rois 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.15","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:15","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Schallum, et la conspiration qu\u2019il forma, cela est \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.16","name":"2 Rois 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.14","name":"2 Rois 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.16","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:16","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Alors Menahem frappa Thiphsach et tous ceux qui y \u00e9taient, avec son territoire depuis Thirtsa; il la frappa parce qu\u2019elle n\u2019avait pas ouvert ses portes, et il fendit le ventre de toutes les femmes enceintes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.17","name":"2 Rois 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.15","name":"2 Rois 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.17","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:17","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>La trente-neuvi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Azaria, roi de Juda, Menahem, fils de Gadi, r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl. Il r\u00e9gna dix ans \u00e0 Samarie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.18","name":"2 Rois 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.16","name":"2 Rois 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.18","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:18","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel; il ne se d\u00e9tourna point, tant qu\u2019il v\u00e9cut, des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, qui avait fait p\u00e9cher Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.19","name":"2 Rois 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.17","name":"2 Rois 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.19","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:19","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Pul, roi d\u2019Assyrie, vint dans le pays; et Menahem donna \u00e0 Pul mille talents d\u2019argent, pour qu\u2019il l\u2019aid\u00e2t \u00e0 affermir la royaut\u00e9 entre ses mains.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.20","name":"2 Rois 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.18","name":"2 Rois 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.20","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:20","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Menahem leva cet argent sur tous ceux d\u2019Isra\u00ebl qui avaient de la richesse, afin de le donner au roi d\u2019Assyrie; il les taxa chacun \u00e0 cinquante sicles d\u2019argent. Le roi d\u2019Assyrie s\u2019en retourna, et ne s\u2019arr\u00eata pas alors dans le pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.21","name":"2 Rois 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.19","name":"2 Rois 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.21","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:21","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Menahem, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.22","name":"2 Rois 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.20","name":"2 Rois 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.22","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:22","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Menahem se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res. Et Pekachia, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.23","name":"2 Rois 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.21","name":"2 Rois 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.23","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:23","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>La cinquanti\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Azaria, roi de Juda, Pekachia, fils de Menahem, r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 Samarie. Il r\u00e9gna deux ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.24","name":"2 Rois 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.22","name":"2 Rois 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.24","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:24","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel; il ne se d\u00e9tourna point des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, qui avait fait p\u00e9cher Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.25","name":"2 Rois 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.23","name":"2 Rois 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.25","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:25","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>P\u00e9kach, fils de Remalia, son officier, conspira contre lui; il le frappa \u00e0 Samarie, dans le palais de la maison du roi, de m\u00eame qu\u2019Argob et Ari\u00e9; il avait avec lui cinquante hommes d\u2019entre les fils des Galaadites. Il fit ainsi mourir Pekachia, et il r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.26","name":"2 Rois 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.24","name":"2 Rois 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.26","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:26","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Pekachia, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela est \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.27","name":"2 Rois 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.25","name":"2 Rois 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.27","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:27","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>La cinquante-deuxi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Azaria, roi de Juda, P\u00e9kach, fils de Remalia, r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 Samarie. Il r\u00e9gna vingt ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.28","name":"2 Rois 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.26","name":"2 Rois 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.28","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:28","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel; il ne se d\u00e9tourna point des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, qui avait fait p\u00e9cher Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.29","name":"2 Rois 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.27","name":"2 Rois 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.29","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:29","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Du temps de P\u00e9kach, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, Tiglath-Pil\u00e9ser, roi d\u2019Assyrie, vint et prit Ijjon, Abel-Beth-Maaca, Janoach, K\u00e9desch, Hatsor, Galaad et la Galil\u00e9e, tout le pays de Nephthali, et il emmena captifs les habitants en Assyrie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.30","name":"2 Rois 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.28","name":"2 Rois 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.30","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:30","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Os\u00e9e, fils d\u2019\u00c9la, forma une conspiration contre P\u00e9kach, fils de Remalia, le frappa et le fit mourir; et il r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place, la vingti\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de Jotham, fils d\u2019Ozias.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.31","name":"2 Rois 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.29","name":"2 Rois 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.31","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:31","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Le reste des actions de P\u00e9kach, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela est \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.32","name":"2 Rois 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.30","name":"2 Rois 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.32","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:32","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.033,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Jotham, roi de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 32-38: cf. 2 Ch 27. Mi 1:1.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>La seconde ann\u00e9e de P\u00e9kach, fils de Remalia, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, Jotham, fils d\u2019Ozias, roi de Juda, r\u00e9gna.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.33","name":"2 Rois 15:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.31","name":"2 Rois 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.33","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:33","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Il avait vingt-cinq ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna seize ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Jeruscha, fille de Tsadok.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.34","name":"2 Rois 15:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.32","name":"2 Rois 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.34","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:34","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel; il agit enti\u00e8rement comme avait agi Ozias, son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.35","name":"2 Rois 15:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.33","name":"2 Rois 15:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.35","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:35","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Seulement, les hauts lieux ne disparurent point; le peuple offrait encore des sacrifices et des parfums sur les hauts lieux. Jotham b\u00e2tit la porte sup\u00e9rieure de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.36","name":"2 Rois 15:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.34","name":"2 Rois 15:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.36","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:36","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Jotham, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois de Juda?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.37","name":"2 Rois 15:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.35","name":"2 Rois 15:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.37","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:37","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Dans ce temps-l\u00e0, l\u2019\u00c9ternel commen\u00e7a \u00e0 envoyer contre Juda Retsin, roi de Syrie, et P\u00e9kach, fils de Remalia.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.38","name":"2 Rois 15:38","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.36","name":"2 Rois 15:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.38","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 15:38","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.016.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.15.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Jotham se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et il fut enterr\u00e9 avec ses p\u00e8res dans la ville de David, son p\u00e8re. Et Achaz, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15","name":"2 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.16.1","name":"2 Rois 16:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.16.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.37","name":"2 Rois 15:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb58de4a0.98127723');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb58de4a0.98127723\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb58de4a0.98127723","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb58de4a0.98127723'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb58de4a0.98127723\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}